text: Sud (South) or Sud-Muntenia is a development region in Romania. The capital of the South Development Region is Călăraşi. County population 2011 Argeș 614,914 Călărași 287,269 Dâmbovița 510,287 Giurgiu 267,147 Ialomița 265,559 Prahova 754,541 Teleorman 369,897 Total 3,069,614 Source: == References == Category:Development regions of Romania
title: Sud (development region)
